
A Wordpress plugin to push leads to your onepagecrm.com account

== Description ==

Push leads to your OnePageCRM account through a form on your site.

The plugin allows you to capture a Lead's Name, Company, Phone, Email and a message. 

New leads are given an Urgent "Next Action", along with a message of "Web Contact: Callback". 
You have the option of selecting a OnePageCRM tag you have set up to add to new leads 
(useful for identifying leads coming through your site).


== Installation ==

1. Upload the directory `aaOnepage` to the `/wp-content/plugins/` directory
2. Activate the plugin through the 'Plugins' menu in WordPress
3. Visit the plugin settings and sign into your onepage account
4. use the shortcode [aa_onepage_form] in a WordPress Page or Post, or place `<?php echo aa_onepage_form(); ?>` in your template


